                  </persName>
            ; the two watchman, Wilson and Welch, took the other two; they were going all the same way, about twenty or thirty yards asunder, that is, 
               <persName id="t17700530-20-person181">
                  James
                   Atherton
               <interp inst="t17700530-20-person181" type="surname" value="Atherton"></interp>
