                     <interp inst="t17700530-20-person190" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I live near Mr. Bunyan. I have known Delaforce eleven years: he always bore a good character.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17700530-20-person191">
